# Installation

```
~/.dotfiles/install

cat ~/.dotfiles/zypper/*.txt | xargs sudo zypper install

pip3 install --break-system-packages -r ~/.dotfiles/python/requirements.txt

sudo ln -s ~/.dotfiles/scripts/ssh-askpass-xfce4-terminal /usr/bin/ssh-askpass

sudo ln -s ~/.dotfiles/cron/clear_downloads /etc/cron.daily/clear_home_petr_downloads

sudo ln -s ~/.dotfiles/cron/clear_dropbox /etc/cron.daily/clear_home_petr_dropbox

sudo ln -s ~/.dotfiles/cron/clear_work_logs /etc/cron.daily/clear_home_petr_work_logs
```

## rbenv

```
curl -fsSL https://github.com/rbenv/rbenv-installer/raw/HEAD/bin/rbenv-installer | bash
rbenv install -l
```

## nvm

```
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/master/install.sh | bash
```

## Neovim

```
sh -c 'curl -fLo "${XDG_DATA_HOME:-$HOME/.local/share}"/nvim/site/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs \
       https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim'
```

open `nvim` and run `:PlugInstall` and `:UpdateRemotePlugins`

## Double commander

Download qt-latest from https://download.opensuse.org/repositories/home:/Alexx2000:/doublecmd-svn/AppImage to `~/Applications`
